theorem Topology.closure_eq_interior_union_frontier {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    closure (A : Set X) = interior (A : Set X) ∪ frontier (A : Set X) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hxCl
    by_cases hxInt : x ∈ interior (A : Set X)
    · exact Or.inl hxInt
    ·
      have hxFront : x ∈ frontier (A : Set X) := And.intro hxCl hxInt
      exact Or.inr hxFront
  · intro hxUnion
    cases hxUnion with
    | inl hxInt =>
        exact subset_closure hxInt
    | inr hxFront =>
        exact hxFront.1
